{"tid":1353964,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"食緊飯，有點感動，班廢老終於屌政府","createTime":"2019-07-23T05:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T09:44:30.000Z","uid":23815,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"01942c603854379dcd62016aa7549ebdfa34c943","tid":1353964,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:05:33.000Z","msg":"屋村大排檔，都預左班廢老會話各路英雄<br />\n同枱既廢老終於都肯鬧政府<br />\n雖然都聽得出佢地有啲好愛國<br />\n但發表既言論都好欣慰 起碼之前既事唔係白做<br />\n<br />\n1. 兩名老男人<br />\n<br />\n個女人 (M記男孩個老母 ) 比人起底係一定架啦，咁樣走出黎咁激動一係痴線，一係做戲<br />\n但個政府都無撚用，做既野都唔係為市民<br />\n太平盛世下既問題根本無去了解過，無論係保皇定後生<br />\n盧偉聰無撚用，警察唔係維持治安，收到黑吃黑，成個警隊都縮到傻閪，你應該知真定假，要強硬啲，搞到全城恐慌<br />\n<br />\n2. 另外2個男人<br />\n警務處處長都無撚用，明知國徽咁重要都唔派兵守住，明知一定有人搞<br />\n比我逗廿萬一個月，我都識分重要唔重要<br />\n<br />\n沙中線、高鐵超支，講就話為香港好，但最重要既教育醫療又唔比錢搞好<br />\n啲錢全部都係我地稅收，但自己無分用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>雖然佢地都好愛國<br />\n但睇黎香港人既聲音都開始傳到入廢老耳中 開始有些少覺醒<br />\n大家都要繼續加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3d34a4b15ceda9e1082bef207251e79b4a6900c5","tid":1353964,"uid":45041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:08:42.000Z","msg":"繼續加油"},{"pid":"39a55fe45dbb9adef2133b4ffaab9614d8f85f94","tid":1353964,"uid":79182,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:10:44.000Z","msg":"焦土派覺得好滿意<br />\n反正示威者點都會俾人屌架啦<br />\n一於等政府警犬都俾人屌<br />\nIF WE BURN<br />\nYOU BURN WITH US"},{"pid":"5b4ee7121030e35224aa850febced9002632c502","tid":1353964,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39a55fe45dbb9adef2133b4ffaab9614d8f85f94","tid":1353964,"uid":79182,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:10:44.000Z","msg":"焦土派覺得好滿意<br />\n反正示威者點都會俾人屌架啦<br />\n一於等政府警犬都俾人屌<br />\nIF WE BURN<br />\nYOU BURN WITH US"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 令槍頭指向林病同聰聰"},{"pid":"194784245ffb50f0ad4434c976c586cc55eed15a","tid":1353964,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}